info.name: Rental Store - V1
info.description: This API endpoint is about a store that rents out books and equipment to users. One of the main activity of the endpoint is to get the statistics log of number of items rented or returned over a period of time (e.g. month or a year).

item.name: Users

request.description: Get all users data and relationship with rents table.
